# Generic action used by every script-hosted endpoint on the agent's machine.
# A scripted skill is just an action server with this signature; the agent
# host's script_action_server registers one such action server per registered
# script and advertises them on /script_action_server_<session>/skills so
# the orchestrator's SkillDiscovery picks them up like any hardware proxy.

# Goal — parameter bindings, validated against the script's input_schema
# (declared at register_script time and carried in the SkillAdvertisement).
robot_skills_msgs/KeyValue[] inputs
---
# Result
bool success
string message
robot_skills_msgs/KeyValue[] outputs
---
# Feedback
string status
float32 progress
